graph TB
    subgraph "CodeFlare Operator"
        Manager[Manager Deployment<br/>controller-manager]
        WebhookServer[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]
        RayController[RayCluster Controller]
        AppWrapperController[AppWrapper Controller]
        MetricsServer[Metrics Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]
        HealthProbes[Health Probes<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]
        CertController[Certificate Controller<br/>cert-controller v0.10.1]

        Manager --> RayController
        Manager --> AppWrapperController
        Manager --> WebhookServer
        Manager --> MetricsServer
        Manager --> HealthProbes
        CertController -->|manages certs| WebhookServer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        AppWrapperCR[AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2]
        RayClusterCR[RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1<br/>External - managed by KubeRay]
        KueueWorkloadCR[Workload CR<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1<br/>External - managed by Kueue]
        DSCInitCR[DSCInitialization CR<br/>dscinitialization.opendatahub.io/v1]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicies<br/>Ray cluster traffic control]
        RouteIngress[Routes/Ingress<br/>Ray dashboard access]
        Services[Services<br/>Ray cluster services]
        Secrets[Secrets<br/>mTLS certificates]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KubeRayOperator[KubeRay Operator v1.1.0]
        Kueue[Kueue v0.6.2]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
        Prometheus[Prometheus]
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift only]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| AppWrapperCR
    User -->|creates| RayClusterCR

    AppWrapperCR -->|watched by| AppWrapperController
    RayClusterCR -->|watched by| RayController
    KueueWorkloadCR -->|watched by| AppWrapperController
    DSCInitCR -->|watched by| Manager

    WebhookServer -->|validates/mutates| AppWrapperCR
    WebhookServer -->|validates/mutates| RayClusterCR

    RayController -->|creates| NetworkPolicy
    RayController -->|creates| RouteIngress
    RayController -->|creates| Services
    RayController -->|creates| Secrets

    AppWrapperController -->|creates| KueueWorkloadCR
    AppWrapperController -->|deploys| RayClusterCR

    Manager -->|API calls| K8sAPI
    MetricsServer -->|scraped by| Prometheus

    RayController -.->|depends on| KubeRayOperator
    AppWrapperController -.->|depends on| Kueue
    RayController -.->|injects on OpenShift| OAuthProxy

